><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resumo","title":"Resumo","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<div id=\"sect2\"></div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n<p>A propriedade somente leitura&nbsp;<code><strong>Node.baseURI</strong></code>&nbsp;retorna a URL base absoluta de um nó.</p>\n\n<p>A URL base é usada para <a href=\"https://developers.whatwg.org/urls.html#resolving-urls\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">resolver&nbsp;</a>URLs relativas quando o navegador precisa obter uma URL absoluta, por exemplo, quando processa&nbsp;o atributo&nbsp;<code>src</code> do elemento HTML&nbsp; <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code></a> ou o atributo <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/XLink\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">xlink (en-US)</a>:href</code>&nbsp;do XML.</p>\n\n<p>No caso&nbsp;comum, a URL base é simplesmente a localização do documento, mas ela pode ser afetada por vários fatores, incluindo o elemento&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/base\"><code>&lt;base&gt;</code></a> em&nbsp;HTML&nbsp;e o&nbsp;atributo <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/baseURI\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">xml:base (en-US)</a>&nbsp;em XML.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>baseURI</em> = <em>node</em>.baseURI;\n</pre>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>baseURI</code> é uma&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> que representa&nbsp;a URL base do&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a> especificado. Pode ser <code>null</code> caso não consiga&nbsp;obter uma URL absoluta.</li>\n <li><code><em>node</em>.baseURI</code> é somente leitura.</li>\n <li><code><em>node</em>.baseURI</code> pode mudar com o tempo (ver abaixo).</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"details","title":"Detalhes","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"a_url_base_de_um_documento","title":"A URL base de um documento","isH3":true,"content":"<p>É a URL base de um&nbsp;<em>documento</em>&nbsp;padrão&nbsp;ao&nbsp;endereço do documento&nbsp;( como exibido pelo navegador e disponível em&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window/location\"><code>window.location</code></a> ), mas pode mudar o padrão:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Quando uma tag HTML <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/base\"><code>&lt;base&gt;</code></a> é encontrada no documento;</li>\n <li>Quando esse é um novo documento creado dinamicamente.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Veja a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://developers.whatwg.org/urls.html#base-urls\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">seção&nbsp;URLs base do padrão HTML</a> para mais detalhes.</p>\n\n<p>Você pode usar&nbsp;<code><em><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>document</code></a></em>.baseURI</code>&nbsp; para obter a URL base de um documento. Note que a obtenção da URL base para um documento pode retornar diferentes URLs ao longo do tempo se as tags&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/base\"><code>&lt;base&gt;</code></a> ou a localização do documento mudarem.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"a_url_base_de_um_elemento","title":"A URL base de&nbsp;um&nbsp;elemento","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A&nbsp;URL base de um elemento em HTML&nbsp;é, normalmente,&nbsp;&nbsp;igual&nbsp; a&nbsp;URL base do documento onde o nó está.</p>\n\n<p>Se o documento contém atributos&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/baseURI\">xml:base</a></code> ( que você não deve fazer em documento HTML), o <code><em>element</em>.baseURI</code>&nbsp;recebe&nbsp;os atributos&nbsp;<code>xml:base dos elementos pai </code>into account when computing the base URL. Veja&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/baseURI\">xml:base</a>&nbsp;para mais detalhes.</p>\n\n<p>Você pode usar&nbsp;<code><em><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>element</code></a></em>.baseURI</code> para obter a URL base de um&nbsp;elemento.</p>","titleAsText":"A URL base de um elemento"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Especificação","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"spectable standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-node-baseuri\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'baseURI' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Core/core.html#Node3-baseURI\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 3 Core Specification<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'baseURI' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsoleto</span></td>\n   <td>Introduzida</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_também","title":"Ver&nbsp;também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/base\"><code>&lt;base&gt;</code></a> (HTML)</li>\n <li>Atributo <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/baseURI\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">xml:base (en-US)</a></code>&nbsp;(Documentos XML)</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node.baseURIObject</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> – uma variante desta API para complementos&nbsp;da Mozilla e código&nbsp;interno. Retorna a&nbsp;URL base como uma <code>nsIURI</code></li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"Ver também"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Resumo","id":"resumo"},{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Detalhes","id":"details"},{"text":"Especificação","id":"specification"},{"text":"Ver&nbsp;também","id":"ver_também"}],"summary":"A propriedade somente leitura Node.baseURI retorna a URL base absoluta de um nó.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.baseURI","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Node.baseURI","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.baseURI","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Node.baseURI","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.baseURI","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/node/baseuri","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/node/baseuri/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node","title":"Node"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node/baseURI","title":"Node.baseURI"}],"pageTitle":"Node.baseURI - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}